    <dict>
        <key>default</key>
        <string>Description: Novoker Post-Install Profile. Install this AFTER your app opens successfully to permanently block Apple's revoke servers on Wi-Fi and Cellular.

🔒 Official Website: https://novoker.pages.dev
🌐 Source Code: https://github.com/is9x/novoker</string>
    </dict>
